title: REMOVED: Katina's
typeOfFood: Lacto, Mediterranean, Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Greek, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Greek gyro and pita house. Veg choices include hummus, grape leaves, falafel, spinach pies, vegetarian platter, and a couple sandwich. Vegans need to specify as dairy is used. REMOVED MAY 2016 DUE TO NO VEGAN OPTIONS UNDER NEW OWNERSHIP.
